title: Buy, Sell, or Hold on Minicamp Narratives
itunes:title: Buy, Sell, or Hold on Minicamp Narratives
description:
A room filled with some heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Andrew Luck’s timeline to return, Eric Decker visiting the Titans, and Gregg’s trip to Rams camp. The guys then debate if they would buy, sell or hold on the bigger storylines from minicamp.
